title: Spa-like bathrooms feature, Gated Community, Car Wash
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to The Palmer', 'Unwind at The Palmer, offering spacious one, two and three bedroom floor plans and newly renovated interior features.', "Here you're close to historic Woodstock, shopping, golf, and minutes from downtown Atlanta.", 'Located in the highly rated Cherokee school district, with features like garages and garden baths.', "There's a perfect home for you at The Palmer Apartments.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 707 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Dens', '- Cozy gas & wood-burning fireplaces with charming mantles and slate hearths', '- Double vanities in bathrooms', '- Comforting custom-home features', '- Spa-like bathrooms feature', '- Built-in bookshelves', '- Oversized whirlpool and garden baths', '- Private patio or balcony', 'Community Amenities', '- Redwood dry heat sauna', '- Garages available with remote access', '- Athletic facility with aerobics center', '- Car Wash', '- Dog Park', '- Outdoor stainless steel grill', '- Playground', '- Gated Community', '- Fire Pit', '- Two dazzling swimming pools', '- Lit tennis courts with pavilion', '- Paved walking track', '- 2 picnic areas with grills and tables', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday:1:00PM-5:00PM', 'The Palmer', '1345 Towne Lake Hills S Drive, Woodstock, GA, 30189', 'Tw6CdFVNCur']
